text.tspan: Poison: (4d4 dmg & poisoned [1 min]) or 14 CON save = 1/2 dmg
Can use on 3 arrows or 1 melee weapon for 3 hits.
DARKVISION: Dim -> bright w/i 60' & dark -> dim
HEART: Commoners try to help me & will fight
w/me if I'm alone, unless I'm a danger to them
THIEVES' CANT: 4x longer but can hide messages
CAT'S BURST: 1 turn w/2x speed, move 0' to regain
ASSASSINATE: Adv on attack vs target that hasn't
had a turn yet. Hit on Surprised -> Critical hit
SNEAK ATTACK: if hit w/finesse or range weapon
AND (have Adv on attack OR target w/i 5' of
STRIKE (BA) - Punch after monk weaponm attack
DODGE (1 Ki) - Dodge as a BA
FLURRY (1 Ki) - Punch twice as BA after any attack
Appearance: Born during eclipse; has darker fur;
Radiant followers believe it a bad omen
Distrusts divine beings; guarded around clerics
Not social self-interested. Easily distractable by
shiny items & compulsive if tempted by new info
Items -- even people -- are disposable to me once
exhausted of new info. Spends $$ impulsively.
- The Radiant religious sect & Risers group
- Tabaxi tavern bard from northern road
- Resolution of moral code; develop patience?
Artifacts: an obsidian one, and a green marble-y one
Bag of Holding: barks, snowrose, moss, big yeti pelt <-- from scroll
Climbing Rope: 60' silk rope holds <= 3K#. Animates on action, moves
<= 10' on BA. Can knot & grant Adv to climbs. 20 AC + 20 HP
Disappear Dust: everything w/i 10' becomes invisible for 2d4 minutes.
It also ends if creature makes attack or spell
Elven Boots: make no sound & get Adv on silent mvmt Stealth checks
Healing Potions: Restore HP, Normal (4), Greater (0), Superior (1)
Pyrotechnics Wand: 7 charges, regains 1d6+1/day. d20 on 0, 1 --> gone.
Action to create harmless burst of light w/i 60' & heard 300' away
Scroll: items sought by brotherhood: basilisk stuff, winterwolf pelt
Shield of Faith: one use, grants +2 AC w/concentration
Misc: backpack, BBs, bedroll, bell, candle, crowbar, hammer, hooded
lantern, mess kit, necklace, oil, pitons, 10d rations, ring, string,
+4 to any save w/i 10' of awake Amber
